2007-05-06  Daniel Baumann  <daniel@debian.org>

	* Merging patches from casper 1.81+debian-4, see ChangeLog.casper.
	* conf/live.conf:
	  - Renamed HOST to HOSTNAME.
	* debian/init:
	  - Added quickreboot.
	  - Renamed /cdrom to /live_media.
